[% WRAPPER "_page.tt" WITH title = 'Edinburgh Perl Mongers' %]
  <h2>Edinburgh Perl Mongers</h2>
  <p>
    Mostly an excuse to meet up once a month for a <code>$beverage</code> and chat.  Conversations cover a wide range of subjects, technical and otherwise, so anyone is welcome regardless of accent, color, creed, education, gender, or anything else.
  </p>
    <p>
    Established in July 1999, we're a part of the global <a href="http://www.pm.org/">Perl Monger</a> organisation but we're interested in lots of different languages, tech and topics.
  </p>
  <p>
    We don't care if you know Perl.  There are plenty things to chat about. The only rule is: <b>be chill</b>.
  </p>
  <h2>Events</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Regular social meeting:</b> 4th Thursday of the month. From 6:30pm at <a href="http://www.cumberlandbar.co.uk/">Cumberland Bar</a>.</li>
    <li><b title="Heretics!">Irregular social meeting:</b> 5th Thursday of the month. Check the <a href="http://mail.pm.org/mailman/listinfo/edinburgh-pm">mailing list</a> as venues change.</li>
    <li><a href="http://act.yapc.eu/lpw2013/">London Perl Workshop, Saturday 30th November 2013</a></li>
  </ul>

